# Normalize all text files to LF on checkout (including on Windows), so
# generated/checked-in output (e.g. src/engine/data/generated.ts) matches
# byte-for-byte regardless of platform, and shell scripts don't break under
# `set -euo pipefail` due to stray \r characters.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary

